    "description": "<strong>加入DISCORD</strong><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>以一敌千，寡可敌众</strong></h2><br><strong>欢迎来到《星际幸存者》的免费序章版本，各式飞船、全新武器和战役模式可供体验！</strong><br><br>在茫茫宇宙之中，你驾驶着最后一艘飞船。面对蜂拥而至、无穷无尽的敌人包围，你需要利用飞船的强大武器和舰体升级存活下来。<br><br>🌌 全新 <strong><i>战役</i></strong>模式 - 搭配卡牌，组合武器<br>🌌 全新 <strong><i>无尽</i></strong>模式 - 火力全开，刷新高分<br>🌌 全新 <strong><i>侦察飞船</i></strong>，推进自带护盾<br>🌌 全新 <strong><i>武器</i></strong>3款，更有升级功能<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>无尽宇宙，孤舰前行</strong></h2><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2289280/extras/603b470dec6a7200199e891033ac9f9e.poster.avif?t=1677866344\" width=610 height=342 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2289280/extras/603b470dec6a7200199e891033ac9f9e.webm?t=1677866344\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2289280/extras/603b470dec6a7200199e891033ac9f9e.mp4?t=1677866344\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>《星际幸存者》是一款Roguelike星际生存游戏。你在每局游戏中可以选择不同的武器和升级选项，打造属于自己的强大飞船。同时，你还需要运用物理知识控制飞船，在成千上万敌人的追杀之下突出重围。通过击杀敌人来获取资源，升级武器、飞船，还可以解锁新舰。<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>组合武器，强化飞船</strong></h2><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2289280/extras/eaaaee96ac6a2d29655e34ac9ab675ca.poster.avif?t=1677866344\" width=610 height=340 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2289280/extras/eaaaee96ac6a2d29655e34ac9ab675ca.webm?t=1677866344\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2289280/extras/eaaaee96ac6a2d29655e34ac9ab675ca.mp4?t=1677866344\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>将不同武器装备在飞船的不同位置，并通过武器升级来实现强大的组合效果，将敌人杀个片甲不留！不过别掉以轻心，<strong>随着你变得越来越强，宇宙对你的恶意也会越来越重</strong>。<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>星舰就绪，恭候舰长！</strong></h2><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2289280/extras/d2b42e80fe7f78e71808397a82b92526.avif?t=1677866344\" width=610 height=280 /></span><br>各式飞船可供选择，每艘飞船都有独特的武器组合和游戏体验。<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>卡牌构筑 + 弹幕射击</strong></h2><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2289280/extras/0bd9a901134fa43c03d8514411aa301b.avif?t=1677866344\" width=600 height=338 /></span><br>在<strong><i>挑战</i></strong>模式享受独特的Roguelike体验和乐趣！解锁并购买新卡牌，组建你的卡组——只有预组卡组的卡牌才会出现在你的升级选项中。你也可以在局内升级卡牌，强化你的装备和牌组。<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>星际航行，定制旅程</strong></h2><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2289280/extras/8804b829d5afc039fdcad89a0e45a197.poster.avif?t=1677866344\" width=610 height=342 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2289280/extras/8804b829d5afc039fdcad89a0e45a197.webm?t=1677866344\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2289280/extras/8804b829d5afc039fdcad89a0e45a197.mp4?t=1677866344\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><strong><i>战役</i></strong>模式提供不同任务线程可供选择，在迎战大Boss之前谨慎前行、升级修炼。如果你追求高风险高回报，挑战<strong><i>困难模式</i></strong>可以赚取更多积分。你还可以在<strong><i>无限</i></strong>模式中刷新高分，惊艳全宇宙！<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong><i>喜欢序章吗？</i></strong>将游戏本体也加入愿望单吧！</h2>",
